{"tid":1913681,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"兩個人同床訓障礙","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:41:14.000Z","uid":239146,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"64d2cfd18ce6843f3d03c075eebe9491f701d3fc","tid":1913681,"uid":239146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意同男朋友訓 平時我地都好鐘意攬住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬住一齊訓 好sweet<br />\n但每次攬住訓 我未訓著已經頸緊膊痛<br />\n要轉身啪下條頸 又怕郁會整醒佢 又拍壓住佢隻手會痺<br />\n所以而加一齊訓都係拖住手 或者橋住隻手入睡<br />\n訓到半夜通常會變背對背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實攬住一齊訓有冇咩技巧？或者有咩pose大家都舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbb03bb2018722b14247cd53f22cf6da2f2565c","tid":1913681,"uid":352215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f02e136369dd4b257de1eb5ecbc4ff5bee9b84cc","tid":1913681,"uid":209724,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"插住訓，每兩個鐘轉一次人"},{"pid":"3d1458f1a6aab86765f2c4e7a99fece361d2fccd","tid":1913681,"uid":35143,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"壓住手訓最ON9 <br />\n被壓果方會訓得唔好同埋條頸痛"},{"pid":"6c6ac12cc8120c7b87af105cf8b1f4ec29102517","tid":1913681,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔試下女上男下插住瞓？"},{"pid":"8bd11b0460bca3469b0793a16baebf21798328a5","tid":1913681,"uid":313514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f1b9b38fd35636e77ef23b4d0035e59218e3cd9","tid":1913681,"uid":60563,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"最好既睡眠質素一定係各有各訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拖手仔已經係有身體接觸又keep得好訓既選擇"},{"pid":"5910c2d8d3b37b60632da6eb8d8bccdb9e6241d0","tid":1913681,"uid"